    <item>
      <title>对于新兴市场来说，“明年运气会更好”很难让人接受</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/for-emerging-markets-better-luck-next-year-is-hard-to-believe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专注于新兴市场的投资者在过去一年里没有什么值得庆祝的事情。或者更确切地说，在过去十年里也是如此。现在，唐纳德·特朗普的关税和贸易战的前景让一些人考虑彻底放弃这些投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/for-emerging-markets-better-luck-next-year-is-hard-to-believe</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
